}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This device uses two [[Genesys Logic]] GL850G 4-Port USB Hub controllers. The device presents itself as two seperate 05e3:0608 USB hubs to the host system.
The power adapter included with the device (or at least one device) is a '''Ming Data''' CP0540 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.8A -> 5VDC, 4A).
==Links of Interest== [http://www.randomprojects.org/wiki/Belkin_F5U700_USB_hub On ''Uwe Hermann'''s '''RandomProjects''' Wiki] :[http://www.flickr.com/photos/uwehermann/sets/72157624406963331/ Same photos on Flickr] :"USH-377-061220 v1.0" is silkscreened on the bottom of the board.
